THAT'S ALL THAT LIFE
MEANS TO ME ANYMORE.

19:47.770 --> 19:49.636
THAT'S THE ONLY THING
THAT'S IMPORTANT.

19:49.730 --> 19:52.768
AND, PIP, I PROMISE YOU,
