22:48.492 --> 22:49.527
WANNA COME WITH US?

22:49.618 --> 22:50.904
AH, NO, THANKS.

22:50.995 --> 22:52.736
I'LL JUST
SORTA WALK AROUND.

22:52.830 --> 22:54.787
